{"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"metadata":{"title":"OUDSComponents","modules":[{"name":"OUDSComponents"}],"role":"collection","externalID":"OUDSComponents","symbolKind":"module","roleHeading":"Framework"},"sections":[],"primaryContentSections":[{"content":[{"text":"Overview","level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"Overview"},{"text":"Buttons","type":"heading","anchor":"Buttons","level":3},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSButton","isActive":true},{"text":" propose layout with text only, icon only or text and icon.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"Four hierarchies are proposed for all layouts: "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"default"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"strong"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":", ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"minimal","type":"text"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":" and ","type":"text"},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"negative"}]},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Two style are available: "},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"default","type":"text"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":" and ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"loading","type":"text"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":".","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"If button is placed on colored surface using ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSColoredSurface"},{"text":", the default colors (content, background and border) are automatically adjusted to switch to monochrom.","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"A button with ","type":"text"},{"code":"OUDSButton.Hierarchy.Negative","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" hierarchy is not allowed as a direct or indirect child of an ","type":"text"},{"code":"OUDSColoredSurface","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"codeListing","code":["     \/\/ Icon only with default hierarchy","     OUDSButton(hierarchy: .default, icon: Image(\"ic_heart\")) {}","","     \/\/ Text only with negative hierarchy","     OUDSButton(hierarchy: .negative, text: \"Delete\") {}"],"syntax":"swift"},{"level":3,"text":"Links","anchor":"Links","type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSLink","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" proposes layout with text only or text with icon."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"It also proposes layout to navigate forward or backward."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"The link can be displayed in "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"small"},{"type":"text","text":" or "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"medium"},{"text":" size.","type":"text"}]},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["    \/\/ Text only in small size","    OUDSLink(text: \"Feedback\", size: .small) { \/* the action to process *\/ }","","    \/\/ Text and icon in medium size","    OUDSLink(text: \"Feedback\", icon: Image(\"ic_heart\"), size: .medium) { \/* the action to process *\/ }","","    \/\/ Navigate to previous page with link in a medium size","    OUDSLink(text: \"Back\", arrow: .back, size: .medium) { \/* the action to process *\/ }"]},{"anchor":"Customize-components","text":"Customize components","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"level":3,"text":"Apply a specific shadow effect (elevation tokens)","anchor":"Apply-a-specific-shadow-effect-elevation-tokens","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The unified design system implemented by OUDS iOS library allows to apply "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"elevation effets"}]},{"text":" on a ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"View"},{"text":", i.e. a shadow under the component.","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"Because the design tool in use is ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Figma","type":"text"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":" which defines such shadow with a ","type":"text"},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"blur","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" and a "},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"spread","type":"text"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":" radiuses, and because ","type":"text"},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"SwiftUI"}]},{"text":" uses only its own ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"radius","type":"text"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" definition, an extension of "},{"code":"View","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" has been implemented to let users apply some effect using an ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/ios.unified-design-system.orange.com\/documentation\/oudstokenssemantic\/elevationcompositesemantictoken"},{"text":" from the ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/ios.unified-design-system.orange.com\/documentation\/oudstokenssemantic\/"},{"text":" library thanks to the method ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"shadow(elevation: ElevationCompositeSemanticToken)"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["\/\/ For example, apply the elevation effect \"elevationDragLight\" from your theme:","myView.shadow(elevation: theme.elevationDragLight)","","\/\/ And in the theme this \"elevationDragLight\" has been defined for example like:","@objc open var elevationDragLight: ElevationCompositeSemanticToken { ElevationRawTokens.elevationBottom_3_500 }","ColorRawTokens.colorOpacityBlack400)","","\/\/ And if you look deeper, the raw token \"elevationBottom_3_500\" can be like:","public static let elevationBottom_3_500 = ElevationCompositeRawToken(x: 0, y: 4, blur: 4, color: ColorRawTokens.colorOpacityBlack500)","","\/\/ Blur will be used to compute the radius value"]},{"anchor":"Apply-a-specific-typography-font-tokens","level":3,"type":"heading","text":"Apply a specific typography (font tokens)"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Your application identity can be strongly based on the "},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"typography","type":"text"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" you use, i.e. the font family you choose and other configuration details like the font size or the font weight."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"With OUDS, typography depends to the class size, i.e. wether or not the application is in ","type":"text"},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"compact mode","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" or in "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"regular mode","type":"text"}]},{"text":", and is defined with a ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"https:\/\/ios.unified-design-system.orange.com\/documentation\/oudstokenssemantic\/multiplefontcompositerawtokens","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":". defined in the "},{"identifier":"https:\/\/ios.unified-design-system.orange.com\/documentation\/oudstokenssemantic\/fontsemantictokens\/","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"theme"}]},{"type":"text","text":" contains lots of "},{"code":"MultipleFontCompositeRawTokens","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" listing all the combinations of typography you can apply, and these "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"composite semantic tokens","type":"text"}]},{"text":" use ","type":"text"},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"composite raw tokens"}]},{"text":". For example:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["\/\/ Here is a definition of a semantic token inside the theme for typography \"typeDisplayMedium\":","@objc open var typeDisplayMedium: MultipleFontCompositeRawTokens { ","MultipleFontCompositeRawTokens(compact: FontRawTokens.typeBold750, regular: FontRawTokens.typeBold1050) ","}","","\/\/ And here are the raw tokebs definitions:","public static let typeBold750 = FontCompositeRawToken(size: fontSize750, lineHeight: fontLineHeight850, weight: fontWeightBold)","","public static let typeBold1050 = FontCompositeRawToken(size: fontSize1050, lineHeight: fontLineHeight1150, weight: fontWeightBold)"]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"However the "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"theme"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":" must know which ","type":"text"},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"font family"}]},{"text":" to apply, and this font family can be a ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"custom one"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":" or the ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"system one"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"Thus, we let the users define the font family they want by overriding the "},{"code":"fontFamily","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" property. This value will be used to compute the typography, if not defined the systme font will be used.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Thus, if you want to apply a specific typography to a "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"View"},{"text":", supposing you defined previously the semantic tokens, just call the method you want and gives as parameter the theme (to get the custom font if defined):","type":"text"}]},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["\/\/ Apply typography \"type body default small\"","myView.typeBodyDefaultSmall(theme)","","\/\/ Apply typography \"type label strong X large\"","myView.typeLabelStrongXLarge(theme)","","\/\/ Etc."]},{"text":"Apply a specific border (border tokens)","anchor":"Apply-a-specific-border-border-tokens","level":3,"type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"This module exposes the helper ","type":"text"},{"code":"oudsBorder(style:width:radius:color)","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to apply border semantic tokens on a view in order to define a border effect."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"The helper is available through "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"View"},{"type":"text","text":", and tokens through the provider of the theme."}]},{"syntax":"swift","code":["    @Environment(\\.theme) private var theme","","    var body: some View {","        SomeView()","        .oudsBorder(","             style: theme.borders.borderStyleDefault,","             width: theme.borders.borderWidthThin,","             radius: theme.borders.borderRadiusNone,","             color: theme.colors.colorBorderDefault)","     }"],"type":"codeListing"}],"kind":"content"}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[[]]},"kind":"symbol","schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"topicSections":[{"anchor":"Group","identifiers":["doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSButton","doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSLink"],"title":"Group"},{"title":"Enumerations","identifiers":["doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/AccessibilityFocusable"],"generated":true,"anchor":"Enumerations"},{"generated":true,"title":"Extended Modules","identifiers":["doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/Foundation","doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/SwiftUICore"],"anchor":"Extended-Modules"}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/oudscomponents"]}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The catalog of all components provided by OUDS. It contains also "},{"code":"View","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"tex